{
 "name": "RPlog_Rules_and_Regulations",
 "title": "Rules and Regulations",
 "summary": "Aboard a small borrowed shuttle, Paul Nighman slips into the cargo hold, pleased after stretching his legs planetside, talking to old contacts, and doing a little shopping, while the young Shenner watches anxiously for any sign he was followed. The shuttle's owner Jeralic teases Paul and Shenner about the cramped quarters and raises a practical concern: there are identifying symbols on the hull that need to be painted over before the group goes anywhere, lest they be recognized. With Luke Skywalker also part of the traveling band, the scene turns on the small, careful rules of staying hidden aboard a ship that is not their own.",
